      ecommerce-website-front-end
Use HTML to create the structure of your web pages,
including headers, footers, navigation bars, product listings, product detail pages, shopping cart, and checkout pages. Apply CSS for styling and layout purposes, Implement
responsive design using media queries to ensure your
website is mobile-friendly and adapts to different screen
sizes.
Implement interactivity and dynamic functionalities using
JavaScript. Use JavaScript to enable features like filtering products
based on categories, prices, or ratings without refreshing the
entire page. Create functions to add items to the cart, update quantities, calculate totals, and remove items using JavaScript's DOM
manipulation.
